HOW TO BUILD APPLICATION

1) Building remote-gui with Maven and copying libraries to MPS project

In a directory GUI/remote-gui run maven command:

    mvn clean install -Dskip.distribution=false

This will build GUI and copy builded jar libraries to MPS project KarelG.

2) Running project in MPS
Open project KarelG in MPS and rebuild the whole project.

Panel KarelView should be shown on the right side of MPS IDE.

In solution KarelBasic.sandbox you can run scripts or create a new one.
The script execution should be visible in panel.